Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:01.19,0:00:06.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这不是动画 这不是动画\Nアニメじゃない　アニメじゃない
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:07.19,0:00:10.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是真的\N本当のことさ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:11.79,0:00:14.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在大家都静静睡下的夜晚\Nみんなが寝静まった夜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:14.99,0:00:17.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,从窗口眺望夜空的话\N窓から空を見ていると
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:17.69,0:00:22.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以看到很厉害的东西\Nとっても　すごいものを　見たんだ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:24.59,0:00:27.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大人们都笑者说\N大人は誰も笑いながら
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:27.59,0:00:30.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我电视看太多了\Nテレビの見過ぎと言うけど
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:30.29,0:00:33.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是我绝对绝对\N僕は　絶対に絶対に
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:33.99,0:00:36.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不会说谎\N嘘なんか言ってない
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:38.79,0:00:44.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,决不会用名为常识的眼镜\N常識と言う眼鏡で
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:45.19,0:00:49.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对我们的世界\N僕たちの世界は
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:50.59,0:00:53.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,进行窥视\Nのぞけやしないのさ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:53.59,0:00:56.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,忘记了梦想的\N夢を忘れた
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:57.59,0:01:02.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,古老的地球人啊\N古い地球人よ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:03.59,0:01:06.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这不是动画 这不是动画\Nアニメじゃない　アニメじゃない
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:06.83,0:01:09.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好奇妙的感觉\N不思議な気持ち
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:09.93,0:01:15.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这不是动画 这不是动画\Nアニメじゃない　アニメじゃない
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:16.53,0:01:19.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是真的\N本当のことさ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:21.13,0:01:24.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是真的\N本当のことさ

Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:31.90,0:01:33.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姬娜想逃离亚加玛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:33.87,0:01:35.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抓走洗达当人质
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:35.83,0:01:37.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,加上敌人的集体攻击
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:37.78,0:01:39.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是受不了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:39.71,0:01:42.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且还多了米查那个古怪的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:42.15,0:01:44.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,使ZZ高达的合体一波三折
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:45.10,0:01:47.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是,遇到的障碍愈多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:47.52,0:01:48.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我越是有所成长
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:49.38,0:01:53.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这可算是神给我的考验吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:56.05,0:01:59.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第十八话 哈曼的身影
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.38,0:02:39.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哈曼大人似乎很喜欢夏日\N以前就这样吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:39.55,0:02:41.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的,最近一直...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:43.62,0:02:46.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有时冬天的寒冷也不错啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.99,0:02:58.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,古利明大人来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.31,0:03:00.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是吗?叫他进来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:01.07,0:03:03.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好久不见,哈曼大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.34,0:03:05.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦你了,古利明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:05.60,0:03:07.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的活跃表现我听说了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.31,0:03:09.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不,我把安多拉弄沉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.97,0:03:11.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说起来真是惭愧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.55,0:03:14.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别在意\N当成负高额保险费就可以了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.98,0:03:16.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.28,0:03:18.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,港口那边似乎很热闹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.74,0:03:21.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,主力部队在做降落地球的准备
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.20,0:03:23.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这次我也要去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.35,0:03:25.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哈曼大人要亲临地球?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.55,0:03:27.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我去,会提高士气
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.69,0:03:29.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,泰坦斯已经灭亡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.46,0:03:31.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奥干的组织也疲弱不堪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:31.78,0:03:34.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再敌对势力都再减弱的现在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.57,0:03:37.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是打败地球联邦政府的机会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.87,0:03:40.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此,所以才会直攻地球
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.89,0:03:43.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且我得到有趣的东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.24,0:03:45.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打算带去地球
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.26,0:03:46.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是什么东西?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.44,0:03:48.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,重高达...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.25,0:03:51.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是,有人能使用吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.87,0:03:55.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是有你\N正在组织的新人类部队吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.49,0:03:59.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哈曼大人,那是不实谣言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.51,0:04:01.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,无所谓,重高达给你使用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.89,0:04:03.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,古利明,你也到地球
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.89,0:04:05.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下官当然陪行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.66,0:04:08.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要能为哈曼大人\N当上忙的话...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.33,0:04:09.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不必说客套话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.21,0:04:44.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嘿嘿...真是顺利\N平时放出太多假陨石
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.19,0:04:46.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,活该被我偷跑进来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.78,0:04:50.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,普露普露
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.72,0:04:59.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,胸口好紧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.89,0:05:03.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是很舒服\N但怎么会这样呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.19,0:05:12.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了,是那驾驶员关系!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.95,0:05:14.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ZZ高达的驾驶员来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.43,0:05:21.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.92,0:05:36.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,高达的驾驶员来了\N不会有错的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.74,0:05:39.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,波蕾,这里是宫殿\N你怎么可以随便乱跑?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.85,0:05:41.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我有急事,你别管
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.08,0:05:42.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,波蕾...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.13,0:05:47.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亚古捷斯的人真有活力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.41,0:05:52.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不对,她是例外\N坏例子,你要当作没看到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.50,0:05:54.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我没这么厉害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.83,0:06:02.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我去居住区一下\N波蕾小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.32,0:06:05.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这种东西用搬运机送就行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.59,0:06:07.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么尽叫我们做些无聊事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.46,0:06:09.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们好像蚂蚁\N
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.40,0:06:11.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蚂蚁比我们好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.33,0:06:13.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有时还能找到甜点吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.61,0:06:20.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们得了重力失衡症了\N差劲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.43,0:06:22.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,比查,你没事吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.94,0:06:27.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,开什么玩笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.46,0:06:35.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这混蛋!可恶,可恶,可恶,可恶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.88,0:06:39.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不准浪费食物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.36,0:06:40.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.02,0:06:43.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,比查,我受够这种生活了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.73,0:06:44.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也受不了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.97,0:06:47.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在亚加玛还好过这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.46,0:06:48.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们回去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.28,0:06:50.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,回亚加玛吗?\N是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.14,0:06:52.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不可能,我们拿什么脸回去?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.81,0:06:55.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,动动你的头脑阿,若救出莉娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.87,0:06:58.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样别人就无话可说了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.79,0:07:01.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好,决定了,开始行动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.74,0:07:16.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我好像有点累了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.07,0:07:22.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H00ffff&}请必须进入3区的人家快动作...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.01,0:07:26.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H00ffff&}请必须进入3区的人家快动作...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.32,0:07:29.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H00ffff&}请必须进入3区的人家快动作...{\c}\N好像香格里拉的高级区
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.10,0:07:33.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过就是有一点不太好\N这里没有天空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.54,0:07:34.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大哥哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.70,0:07:40.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是来找我的吧,大哥哥\N咦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.62,0:07:43.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是波蕾,你好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.28,0:07:46.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么我好?我们有见过面吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.45,0:07:50.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌...你忘记了吗?\Nㄟ!!!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.64,0:07:53.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起,你认错人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.60,0:07:55.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等~~~
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.05,0:07:57.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在赶路,再见
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.81,0:08:00.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行!我们要在一起!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.45,0:08:05.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,放手!很辛苦啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.94,0:08:10.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,刚才那个人很像捷度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.60,0:08:12.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不可能,不过有点像
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.74,0:08:26.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又是苹果
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.11,0:08:32.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉,惊扰大家了\N这个苹果很好吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.21,0:08:34.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是这里的老板吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.78,0:08:36.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让你久等了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.08,0:08:36.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.03,0:08:38.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你吃的完吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.82,0:08:39.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当然
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.06,0:08:41.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,干什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.41,0:08:42.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你拿着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.55,0:08:48.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ㄚ~~~我要吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.28,0:08:53.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好好吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.71,0:08:57.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以前我也来过这家店
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.93,0:09:01.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.16,0:09:03.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎样,亚古捷斯的街道很美吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:03.93,0:09:05.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.84,0:09:09.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有时间应该带你慢慢参观
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.06,0:09:13.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是服饰店!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.23,0:09:14.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想要买衣服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.91,0:09:16.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,衣服?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.53,0:09:19.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对了,以后还要\N离开亚古捷斯一段时间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.12,0:09:21.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,确实应该添购衣服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.20,0:09:24.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂!听在那家店前面\N是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.42,0:09:25.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大哥哥叫什么名子?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.84,0:09:28.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,捷度,捷度.桑达
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.44,0:09:32.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是第一殖民地\N香格里拉的人吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.63,0:09:34.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是土生土长的亚古捷斯人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.46,0:09:36.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,头一次这么近看着你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.73,0:09:40.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么认识我的?\N这样说太奇怪了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.10,0:09:42.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊,确实奇怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.09,0:09:44.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜托你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.52,0:09:45.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:45.26,0:09:46.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来接吻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:48.25,0:09:51.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等一下,刚见面就接吻太快了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.30,0:09:55.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是来找妹妹的,别妨碍我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.42,0:09:59.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,找妹妹...不会是她吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.78,0:10:01.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.00,0:10:03.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想应该是她\N她在哪里?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.05,0:10:04.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.29,0:10:04.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.97,0:10:07.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要!还没全部吃完
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.14,0:10:08.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我来吃完
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.65,0:10:12.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我厉害,沾到脸颊了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.36,0:10:16.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯...这件应该很适合露卡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.93,0:10:19.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是我还不知道她的三围...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.68,0:10:22.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莉娜!怎么了...?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:23.74,0:10:24.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,逃是没用的...!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.22,0:10:26.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这些苹果怎么办?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.77,0:10:28.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卖给别的水果摊吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.73,0:10:30.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个老板真狠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.75,0:10:33.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们已经够琼\N还逼人买这么多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.50,0:10:35.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那不是莉娜吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.48,0:10:40.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莉娜!你在那里做什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.57,0:10:43.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,比查,莫迪,有人在追我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.00,0:10:44.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莉娜!你在那里?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.84,0:10:46.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这边走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:46.30,0:10:48.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,躲是没用的,立刻给我出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.91,0:10:52.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要不要苹果,这个免费送你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.98,0:10:53.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.46,0:10:57.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有点可惜...\N快点,莉娜!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.11,0:11:00.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小偷!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.07,0:11:07.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下车!这辆车被军方征收了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.03,0:11:10.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,像刚才这样一口气吃光
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.25,0:11:14.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不吃光我就不带你去找她\N表演给我看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.29,0:11:15.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.33,0:11:26.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.77,0:11:28.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,照约定的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.37,0:11:30.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,告诉我妹妹在哪里?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.02,0:11:33.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.19,0:11:35.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没关系,这样比较舒服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.37,0:11:42.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想跑!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.01,0:11:45.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,暴走族吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.69,0:11:47.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亚古捷斯也有这种人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.93,0:11:49.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样才有朝气啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.45,0:11:50.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这边 这边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.24,0:12:00.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好!要得到那架MS
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.57,0:12:14.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊!?你们在干什么!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.71,0:12:16.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个MS我开走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.81,0:12:18.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个不是玩具
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.32,0:12:19.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,比查,没问题吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.89,0:12:22.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我操纵这种MS技术比捷度还好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.87,0:12:26.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我看到哥哥了\N那个人一定是哥哥没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:26.78,0:12:29.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不会错的\N我们看到的人一定是捷度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.80,0:12:30.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下来!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:30.91,0:12:32.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.15,0:12:33.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,开动MS的严重性吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.74,0:12:34.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我才不管
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.08,0:12:37.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.73,0:12:40.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.03,0:12:47.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你以为这样乱玩\N不会受到惩罚吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.61,0:12:48.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.55,0:12:49.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是谁在开动那个MS?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.98,0:12:51.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是一群坏小孩啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.59,0:12:54.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是二男一女,对不对?\N是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.36,0:12:58.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莉娜!你再不下来\N别怪我对你使用体罚啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.34,0:13:00.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他说要动用体罚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.55,0:13:01.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个怪小子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.76,0:13:03.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我才不下去啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.25,0:13:04.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,比查,踩死他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.67,0:13:06.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.91,0:13:08.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.35,0:13:12.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莉娜!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.40,0:13:15.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不要追上来,我就饶你一命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:16.63,0:13:18.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,舱门关不起来吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.57,0:13:20.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,开关是这个吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.05,0:13:21.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这架MS
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.03,0:13:22.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还没装舱门
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.66,0:13:25.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样子无法出去啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.40,0:13:27.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,途中在抢太空衣就行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.79,0:13:28.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.14,0:13:32.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么?怎么有MS在市区走动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.92,0:13:34.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他在干什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.19,0:13:37.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊!!!是上次捉弄我们的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:39.98,0:13:41.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可恶!没打中!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.04,0:13:43.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,住手,杀人是不好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.03,0:13:45.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不知道他们对我们多恶劣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.65,0:13:46.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们该死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.85,0:13:49.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,开MS攻击一般人太过份了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.18,0:13:50.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,放走,莉娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.28,0:13:51.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们的作法太卑鄙了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.93,0:13:54.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们全是卑鄙小人\N不行!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.07,0:14:02.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害!跟宫殿一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.48,0:14:05.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莉娜真的再这里吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.64,0:14:08.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊,快点走啊\N喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.15,0:14:14.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦你们了\N是!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.85,0:14:16.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你好你好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.74,0:14:20.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不会是这所宫殿的公主吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.66,0:14:22.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有点不同的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.72,0:14:36.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个感觉...是马沙吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.69,0:14:39.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不...不对,是谁呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.15,0:14:44.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莉娜在哪里?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.47,0:14:45.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在感觉不到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.97,0:14:47.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,感觉不到?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.29,0:14:48.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,洗个澡睡一下好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.65,0:14:50.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样我就可以感觉到,明白吗??
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.83,0:14:52.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.66,0:14:55.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好,我去洗澡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.80,0:15:06.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,开什么玩笑,真是的\N波蕾...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:07.50,0:15:08.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.10,0:15:16.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莉娜真的在这里吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.86,0:15:18.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是谁?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.87,0:15:20.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说出所属的组织跟密码
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.77,0:15:24.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是...再见!\N别跑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.52,0:15:31.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没路了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.10,0:15:34.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打不开\N在这边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.48,0:15:36.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,糟了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.00,0:15:53.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,捷度...人呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.43,0:16:02.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好痛,好痛,好痛~
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:04.01,0:16:06.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,干什么在这里种玫瑰啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.19,0:16:19.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,难道...这小孩...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:20.51,0:16:24.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我来问你,你是哪里的人?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.34,0:16:27.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起,这地方太大了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.61,0:16:31.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你属于什么机关?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:31.41,0:16:32.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别想装傻,你是谁?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.79,0:16:33.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哈曼大人!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:36.10,0:16:38.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我再问一次\N你属于什么机关?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.25,0:16:42.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你问我,我也不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.06,0:16:43.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这次不是恐吓阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.72,0:16:45.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别...开枪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.95,0:16:52.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:53.87,0:16:55.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不说嘛?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.54,0:16:57.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别跑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.29,0:17:00.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:00.95,0:17:03.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,逃向宫殿那里啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.73,0:17:05.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好可惜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:05.28,0:17:06.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋,别逃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.72,0:17:08.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你以大欺小,太差劲了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:08.61,0:17:10.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不知道我们吃了多少苦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:10.39,0:17:13.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你吃的好还有钢琴弹\N让开
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.44,0:17:18.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要踩死你们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:19.57,0:17:21.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了?比查
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:21.52,0:17:22.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拉杆掉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:23.77,0:17:24.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想个办法阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:24.89,0:17:27.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我没办法停下来阿\N快停下来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.73,0:17:33.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.77,0:17:37.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,站住
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:38.92,0:17:40.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我属亚加玛,知道吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:43.40,0:17:45.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亚加玛,果然是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:46.28,0:17:48.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亚古捷斯被
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.71,0:17:50.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亚加玛的人闯进来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:52.40,0:17:53.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别跑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.52,0:17:54.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋才不跑!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:03.44,0:18:04.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.83,0:18:08.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个女人是谁?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:08.39,0:18:09.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我怎么看到奇怪的景象?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:21.24,0:18:24.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是我在月月看到的那艘船
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:24.21,0:18:26.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了,莉娜在那里面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:31.08,0:18:35.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,叔叔\N你有没有看到在这里的陨石
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:35.48,0:18:38.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,陨石?那东西碍事,丢掉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.07,0:18:39.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦!!丢在哪里?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:39.91,0:18:41.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,舱口的另一边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:41.91,0:18:45.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,舱口的另一边...怎么会这样?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:46.04,0:18:48.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你没穿太空衣想去哪里?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:49.50,0:18:50.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这里的另一边吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:56.71,0:19:00.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知道有没有空气?在哪里?\N找到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:05.99,0:19:08.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快没空气了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:16.51,0:19:19.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莉娜一定还再那艘船上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:19.05,0:19:20.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她跑到哪里去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.16,0:19:21.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,捷度!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:24.65,0:19:26.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要去哪里?捷度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:27.14,0:19:29.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是波蕾吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:29.24,0:19:30.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,答对了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.28,0:19:33.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你会操作MS吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:34.70,0:19:36.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么跑出来的,捷度?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:36.74,0:19:40.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你妹妹在宫殿的后院...\N咦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:40.20,0:19:42.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她在地落的MS里头
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:42.63,0:19:45.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能?你骗人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:47.86,0:19:51.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别管你妹妹,和我玩,出来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:51.52,0:19:54.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别开玩笑了,我没有穿太空衣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.31,0:19:56.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也没有,这样很公平
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.58,0:19:58.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才不公平!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:00.74,0:20:01.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,捷度!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:03.15,0:20:03.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:06.26,0:20:07.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,捷度!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:07.56,0:20:08.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,伊莱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:10.32,0:20:12.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想妨碍我与捷度?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:20.14,0:20:22.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,住手,别打了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:22.33,0:20:25.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要生气,我想跟捷度玩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:35.86,0:20:36.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,伊莱!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:37.32,0:20:40.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,住手,波蕾,不然我真的生气了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:40.31,0:20:42.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,捷度,为什么...?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:44.31,0:20:47.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:50.08,0:20:50.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:53.23,0:20:53.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,捷度?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:55.33,0:20:58.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,趁现在,捷度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:04.55,0:21:07.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,波蕾,你不应该杀人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:08.19,0:21:11.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,像你这么天真的女孩\N不该当驾驶员的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:11.10,0:21:11.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,捷度...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:23.66,0:21:26.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只是想跟你玩阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:29.79,0:21:31.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,波蕾,别太过分了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:44.10,0:21:47.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,捷度很讨厌\N为什么不陪我玩?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:47.33,0:21:49.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你坐MS我才不陪你玩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:49.84,0:21:52.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌,很讨厌你阿,我讨厌捷度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:54.93,0:21:57.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂!波蕾!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:58.21,0:22:02.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,算了,我找古利明安慰我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:02.01,0:22:05.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,捷度是大笨蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:11.18,0:22:12.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,连这么小的女孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:12.75,0:22:15.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都被培训成MS驾驶员
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:17.85,0:22:19.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,捷度,你去哪里?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:19.88,0:22:21.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莉娜还在亚古捷斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:22.90,0:22:24.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这次我一定要救出她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:24.78,0:22:26.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你替我转告亚加玛吧

Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:45.10,0:22:50.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在没有道路的荒野里\N道もない荒れた原野に
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:52.10,0:22:58.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,建造铁路真是一件辛苦差事\Nレールを作るのは苦しいことさ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:00.10,0:23:01.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是\Nだけど
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:02.50,0:23:07.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不可以不知晓远方\N遠い向こうも知らなくちゃいけない
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:08.70,0:23:15.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为我们的路现在才开始\N僕達は これからなんだ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:15.80,0:23:24.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人们都说我们是“忘记了梦想的小孩子”\N“夢を忘れた子供達”と 人は言う
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:25.50,0:23:32.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊啊 时代正在哭泣\Nああー 時代が泣いている

Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:46.66,0:23:48.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以ZZ作为见面礼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:48.61,0:23:51.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,进入亚古捷斯也是为了莉娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:51.74,0:23:54.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是 没想到比查和蒙德会把ZZ带出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:54.81,0:24:00.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然后 亚加玛要测试新的主炮\N被设定为目标的怎么是我？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:01.16,0:24:02.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,醒醒啊 波蕾！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:03.76,0:24:05.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下集 高达ZZ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:06.01,0:24:07.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,波蕾与亚古捷斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:08.09,0:24:09.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别攻击啊！布拉度舰长
